                    },
                    "message": "This commit https://github.com/openbmc/phosphor-post-code-manager/commit/8290e0f3297a2c5cbaa8d872d5cf8e19166ca177 improved the performance significantly. Have you tested with it?\nHaving said that, adding a timer can further improve the performance when there is a burst of data. "
                },
                {
                    "file": "/PATCHSET_LEVEL",
                    "line": 0,
                    "reviewer": {
                        "name": "DelphineCCChiu",
                        "email": "Delphine_CC_Chiu@wiwynn.com",
                        "username": "DelphineCCChiu"
                    },
                    "message": "Thanks.\n\nWe will test with it."
