                    "reviewer": {
                        "name": "Kuiying Wang",
                        "email": "wangkuiying.wky@alibaba-inc.com",
                        "username": "kuiyingw"
                    },
                    "message": "I don't think it is a good solution to add timer logic into savePostCodes function, but to a dedicated one.\nYou could reference the timer callback solution in the dbus-sensers implementation for a sensor data updating."
                },
                {
                    "file": "src/post_code.cpp",
                    "line": 75,
                    "reviewer": {
                        "name": "DelphineCCChiu",
